and none of their weaknesses.

276
00:36:02,995 --> 00:36:06,293
Ah... except of the thirst.

277
00:36:06,545 --> 00:36:10,670
The thirst is what controls
all omines nocturni.

278
00:36:11,635 --> 00:36:14,091
