290
00:36:58,586 --> 00:37:01,721
Well, I will tell you,

291
00:37:01,936 --> 00:37:04,682
he hasn't stayed in
one place very long.

292
00:37:05,897 --> 00:37:13,152
Here uh,
the only address he ever had.

293
00:39:23,618 --> 00:39:25,362
