There's our girl.

369
00:44:22,287 --> 00:44:25,991
Of course, Chief Edwards.
We always look after our friends.

370
00:44:34,255 --> 00:44:35,883
Dr Dideo.

371
00:44:36,347 --> 00:44:38,263
Fire chief, councilman.

372
00:44:40,596 --> 00:44:43,010
That's the man right there.

373
00:44:43,978 --> 00:44:46,100
It's like stepping
back in time.

374
00:44:46,316 --> 00:44:47,680
Exactly.

375
00:44:48,685 --> 00:44:50,190
She's gonna do it !

376
00:44:50,448 --> 00:44:51,520
This building,

377
00:44:51,738 --> 00:44:57,120
none would have been possible if it
wasn't for the efforts of ten coming up
pioneers in the automotive industry.

378
00:44:57,155 --> 00:44:58,281
Come on.

379
00:44:58,747 --> 00:45:07,163
I am simply...
following the legacy they left.

380
00:45:08,707 --> 00:45:11,670
Oh, don't be so modest.

381
00:45:12,467 --> 00:45:15,341
They say you're the man
who's gonna save Detroit.

382
