down and replaced.

393
00:45:51,716 --> 00:45:53,832
It's a wasteful cycle.

394
00:45:54,548 --> 00:45:58,053
There's only one thing this country
values when it comes to old age.

395
00:45:59,517 --> 00:46:03,592
So, try to recapture the past ?

396
00:46:03,847 --> 00:46:05,971
Just try not to forget it.

397
00:46:07,107 --> 00:46:08,930
Me either.

398
00:46:15,406 --> 00:46:16,982
