399
00:46:17,236 --> 00:46:18,862
So much to tell.

400
00:46:19,075 --> 00:46:21,320
Well, you could just
start with a name.

401
00:46:22,998 --> 00:46:24,490
Katherine.

402
00:46:25,746 --> 00:46:27,280
Katherine ?

403
00:46:29,457 --> 00:46:36,212
