bright or assertive.

410
00:46:56,738 --> 00:46:59,772
But he was desperate.

411
00:47:00,275 --> 00:47:03,242
Desperate for some sort
of control of his life.

412
00:47:03,405 --> 00:47:04,323
Let go.

413
00:47:04,577 --> 00:47:07,991
People like him are always
taking never giving,

414
00:47:08,248 --> 00:47:10,282
