people around him.

415
00:47:10,537 --> 00:47:13,541
Sucking a life from them.

416
00:47:14,717 --> 00:47:16,373
Honestly,

417
00:47:16,795 --> 00:47:18,291
he's better off.

418
00:47:18,926 --> 00:47:21,211
