450
00:50:11,725 --> 00:50:14,340
I don't care how
fast vampires are.

451
00:50:14,648 --> 00:50:18,762
You can't dodge with a bullet moving
2000 meters per second and trust me,

452
00:50:20,977 --> 00:50:24,102
